WEBVTT

00:06.037 --> 00:08.905
What, exactly, do we suspect
Detective Maguire of doing?

00:08.907 --> 00:10.707
You step in, play the husband,

00:10.709 --> 00:13.070
then you bed my wife, make her pregnant,

00:13.071 --> 00:14.711
and then take her to the abortion doctor!

00:14.713 --> 00:16.413
Kill me now.

00:16.415 --> 00:17.881
I killed my own daughter.

